message: This file contains all necessary information in order to calculate the note count, life required, hands-on life required, and hands-on achieve rate of a song difficulty. Since version 1.20.0, the life required = note_count * 80 - hold_end_count * 30 - tick_count * 50. (1.19.0: note_count * 80 - hold_end_count * 30 - tick_count * 30, and before 1.19.0: note_count * 80 - tick_count * 50)
